I figure that the only time it is expected of someone to lift bags of flour at the bakery is if the person worked there (I picked 'baker' as the best role for that scenario). And for "Unexpected", I was trying to convey that a person who does NOT work at the bakery shouldn't be touching the flour (or any other ingredients).
